        void parse(URL url,
           RequirementAppender appender)
    throws RequirementsParserException,
           URISyntaxException
        Parse the requirements from the provided URL and append these requirements to the provided requirements manager.
        Parameters:
        url - the resource containing a set of requirements
        appender - the manager to publish the requriements to
        Throws:
        RequirementsParserException - if an error occured while loading the requirements
        URISyntaxException - if the provided URL is invalid
